# Optional: drop your Anthropic API key here and the app will load it automatically.
# If you leave this blank, the app shows a field to paste your key in the browser instead.
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com/  ->  copy this file to ".env"
#
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# The key is used directly from your browser to call the Anthropic API.
# It is never committed (.env is git-ignored) and never sent anywhere but Anthropic.

VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
